Invocation Name: shuffle nine hundred twenty nine
Developer Terms of Use
des: Shuffle929.com is a radio station that plays limited commercials, big music blocks, and provides local weather and local news updates. The station is available for online streaming on all Alexa devices as well as on their website. The music playlist draws from a wide range of genres, primarily consisting of adult contemporary, pop, and rock hits from the late 1960s through at least the 1990s.
